nodes.text: A Mon Calamari male bartender worked in the Frozen Kova cantina on the planet Hynestia. The smuggler Lando Calrissian smuggled thirty barrels of illegal purple glandis flower juice onto Hynestia and gave it to the bartender. The bartender confessed that Calrissian had supplied him with the illegal beverage, and Calrissian was apprehended by the forces of the Hynestian royal family.
